  "input_075_label": "农业土壤碳含量开始年份",
  "input_076_description": "<p>从大规模生物炭活动中产生的二氧化碳移除(CDR)增加总量，其中100％是可以去除碳的最大量。生物炭是一种已被制成木碳并埋存保留碳的有机物，。</p>",
  "input_076_label": "生物炭",
  "input_077_description": "<p>生物炭固存活动开始的年份。</p>",
  "input_077_label": "生物炭开始年份",
  "input_078_description": "<p>每当大气CO<sub>2</sub>当量加倍后，全球温度会上升多少。 IPCC的AR5报告以高置信度预估数值大概在1.5到4.5度以內，並以高置信度预估不可能少于1度，中置信度预估不会超过6度。</p><p>来源IPCC. (2021). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ipcc.ch/report/ar6/wg1/#FullReport\"><i>Climate Change 2021: The Physical Science Basis. Contribution of Working Group I to the Sixth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change.</i></a> Chapter 7, Section 7.5.5.</p>",
  "input_078_label": "气候灵敏度",
  "input_079_description": "<p>由于波浪、海流和水层混合（涡流运动），二氧化碳和热量在海洋中混合的速度发生变化。</p><p>来源Oeschger, H., et al. (1975). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.3402/tellusa.v27i2.9900\">A box diffusion model to study the carbon dioxide exchange in nature.</a> <i>Tellus, 27</i>(2), 168–192.</p>",
  "input_079_label": "海洋混合",
  "input_080_description": "<p>二氧化碳浓度与净初级生产力（NPP）之间关系的强度。比值越高，表示植物在生长的过程中二氧化碳浓度增加时可以生长的越快，直到二氧化碳的施肥极限。这个值代表一部分二氧化碳浓度变化之下所解释的净初级生产力变化。这个比率被校准为：当二氧化碳是工业化前浓度的两倍时，净生产力提升大约百分之二十。</p><p>来源Goudriaan, J., &amp; Ketner, P. (1984). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/bf00144611\">A simulation study for the global carbon cycle, including man's impact on the Biosphere.</a> <i>Climatic Change</i>, 6(2), 167–192.</p>",
  "input_080_label": "二氧化碳施肥效应",
  "input_082_description": "<p>海洋对于碳的吸收因温度升高而发生的变化。这个数值是温度每升高一个摄氏度时，二氧化碳在海洋中溶解度减少的量。</p><p>来源Friedlingstein, P., et al. (2006). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1175/jcli3800.1\">Climate–carbon cycle feedback analysis: Results from the C4MIP model intercomparison.</a> <i>Journal of Climate, 19</i>(14), 3337–3353.</p>",
  "input_082_label": "碳循环海洋摄取量",
  "input_083_description": "<p>控制温度对生物量和土壤厌氧菌呼吸率的反馈效应的强度，将碳作为甲烷释放到甲烷循环中。温度的升高会根据这个强度增加甲烷的释放。在数值为 0%/年时，温度对生物质和土壤中的碳的甲烷自然通量的速率没有影响。</p><p>来源Friedlingstein, P., et al. (2006). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1175/jcli3800.1\">Climate–carbon cycle feedback analysis: Results from the C4MIP model intercomparison.</a> <i>Journal of Climate, 19</i>(14), 3337–3353.</p>",
  "input_083_label": "温度对甲烷生成作用的影响",
  "input_084_description": "<p>在温度阈值以上的每一度变化中，由于永久冻土和冻土的融化而从土壤中释放出CH<sub>4</sub>的额外速率（见下面的假设）。当温度达到2ºC时，0.1%的默认值将带来额外的50百万吨/年的甲烷排放，而在3ºC时为100百万吨/年。</p><p>高度不确定，但估计范围一致与Schuur, E.A.G., 等人 (2013). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/s10584-013-0730-7\">Expert assessment of vulnerability of permafrost carbon to climate change.</a> <i>Climatic Change 119</i>(2), 359–374。</p>",
  "input_084_label": "温度对冻土和包合物中甲烷排放的影响",
  "input_085_description": "<p>将全球平均表面温度的临界值升高调整到高于工业化之前的水平，该临界值升高会触发永久冻土和包合物中甲烷的释放。低于此临界值温度，这些来源的排放假定为零。高于临界值，则假定排放随温度线性增加。</p><p>数值高度不确定，但是估计的范围与Schuur, E.A.G., et al.（2013）一致。 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/s10584-013-0730-7\">Expert assessment of vulnerability of permafrost carbon to climate change.</a> <i>Climatic Change 119</i>(2), 359–374.</p>",
  "input_085_label": "冻土与包合物的温度临界点",
  "input_087_description": "<p>通过直接空气捕获而被封存后，每年损失的储存碳百分比。基于IPCC的WG1 AR5报告第6章，表6.15，并且根据IPCC的永久性假设，假设存储存损失为0％/年。</p><p>来源IPCC. (2021). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ipcc.ch/report/ar6/wg1/#FullReport\"><i>Climate Change 2021: The Physical Science Basis. Contribution of Working Group I to the Sixth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change.</i></a> Chapter 7, Section 7.5.5.</p>",
  "input_087_label": "硫化流失率",
  "input_088_description": "<p>透过生物碳进行封存后，每年损失的储存碳百分比。根据IPCC的WG1 AR5报告第6章，表6.15，并假设每年约有0.2％的长期损失。</p><p class=\"sources-header\">来源</p><ul>\n<li>IPCC. (2021). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ipcc.ch/report/ar6/wg1/#FullReport\"><i>Climate Change 2021: The Physical Science Basis. Contribution of Working Group I to the Sixth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change.</i></a> Chapter 7, Section 7.5.5.</li>\n<li>Caldecott, B., Lomax, G., &amp; Workman, M. (2015). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:258c4d8e-3ea7-4b72-a24e-44acd01405d1\">Stranded carbon assets and negative emissions technologies [Working paper].</a> In Stranded Assets Programme. Smith School of Enterprise and the Environment, University of Oxford.</li>\n</ul>",
  "input_088_label": "生物炭流失率",
  "input_091_description": "<p>通过农业土壤碳固存活动所固存碳的年度损失百分比。基于IPCC的WG1 AR5报告第6章，表6.15，以及通过优化美国森林数据所确定的典型生物质和土壤释放速率，估计这一数值每年为1％。</p><p>来源IPCC. (2021). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ipcc.ch/report/ar6/wg1/#FullReport\"><i>Climate Change 2021: The Physical Science Basis. Contribution of Working Group I to the Sixth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change.</i></a> Chapter 7, Section 7.5.5.</p>",
  "input_091_label": "农业土壤碳流失率",
  "input_095_description": "<p>生物碳每年可移除的最大二氧化碳量。</p><p>来源The Royal Society &amp; Royal Academy of Engineering. (2018). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://royalsociety.org/-/media/policy/projects/greenhouse-gas-removal/royal-society-greenhouse-gas-removal-report-2018.pdf/\"><i>Greenhouse gas removal.</i></a> p. 67 Table 2.</p>",
  "input_095_label": "生物炭",
  "input_096_description": "<p>每年透过农业土壤碳移除的最大二氧化碳量。</p><p>来源The Royal Society &amp; Royal Academy of Engineering. (2018). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://royalsociety.org/-/media/policy/projects/greenhouse-gas-removal/royal-society-greenhouse-gas-removal-report-2018.pdf/\"><i>Greenhouse gas removal.</i></a> p. 67 Table 2.</p>",
