  "input_221_label": "煤炭，石油，天然气利用调整的年数",
  "input_222_description": "<p>“ 燃煤发电产生的PM2.5排放量。PM2.5排放量是按单位煤耗(EJ)所释放的质量(百万吨)(Mt)来计量的。可以调整此值来反映排放强度的变化(例如Mt/EJ的降低)。排放因子的变化范围允许为默认值的50％到150％。</p><p>来源Klimont, Z., et al. (2017). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.5194/acp-17-8681-2017\">Global anthropogenic emissions of particulate matter including black carbon.</a> <i>Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics</i>, 17(14), 8681–8723.</p>",
